text: Sybra albomaculata is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Breuning in 1939.BioLib.cz - Sybra albomaculata. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. It contains two subspecies, Sybra albomaculata albomaculata and Sybra albomaculata formosana. ==References== albomaculata Category:Beetles described in 1939
title: Sybra albomaculata
